description: The coronavirus outbreak and the lockdown have had a "catastrophic' effect on business, says the airline.
title: Aer Lingus to cut up to 500 jobs due to pandemic
title_page: Aer Lingus to cut up to 500 jobs due to pandemic - BBC News
maintext: "Ireland has failed to take steps that other European member states have taken they have progressively restored transport services and connectivity in response to a European Commission invitation to do so," said an airline statement.
